{"data":[{"id":560601503,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560601503","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545873074,"updated_time":1545873074,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e印象中第一次知乎回答\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下答案的前提建立在\"题主认真提问\"且身份确实\"老师\"所说的高中生\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了很多回答，大多是给题主泼冷水的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么大家要打击一个对数学充满热爱的高中生的信心？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么大家不相信题主所述？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主说的有没有可能？高中生有没有可能证出\"哥德巴赫猜想\"？\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e可能。\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e但可能性微乎其微。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么这么说？且不说\u003cb\u003e多少数学家数学研究工作者投入其中多少时光都未能解决\u003c/b\u003e，也不谈它需要\u003cb\u003e多么坚实渊博的数学知识\u003c/b\u003e，我们假设，假设题主知识水平达到了解决\"哥德巴赫猜想\"的要求，也确确实实解决了这个猜想。那么，题主\u003cb\u003e会不会疑惑于\"能不能保送清北\"，会不会\"考个211 985都难\"，会不会\"偏科\"？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得，大家不信任题主，甚至于讽刺题主，后者的怀疑占得更多。\u003cb\u003e简言之，题主的思想状况不符合解决\"哥猜\"的人的思想状况，解决了猜想的人，不应该会在知乎提出这样的问题。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e即使你失败了，发现自己的证明错了，也不必悲伤，不必自责\u003c/b\u003e，不过是变成\"高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想失败\"而已，不会有人笑话你。\u003cb\u003e你还年轻，还有很多时间去经历\u003c/b\u003e，不是吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你能静下心来，能明白\u003cb\u003e自己需要的其实并不是\"证猜想上清北\"\u003c/b\u003e，那这篇回答我就写得值了。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"印象中第一次知乎回答以下答案的前提建立在\"题主认真提问\"且身份确实\"老师\"所说的高中生看了很多回答，大多是给题主泼冷水的。为什么大家要打击一个对数学充满热爱的高中生的信心？为什么大家不相信题主所述？题主说的有没有可能？高中生有没有可能证出\"哥…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=363\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ce